CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 3, 1945, pg. 11, reads: "Successful Leaders Honored - Members and friends of the First United Church of the Living God will conduct a series of meetings starting Sunday, Nov. 4, through Monday night, Nov. 12, celebrating eighteen years of successful leadership of Elder and Sister Caldwell. The church is located at 107 Williams Street, South Side.  Sister M. L. Kemp is chairman of the celebration committee."
TitMainTitle: Josie Caldwell and Samuel Caldwell posed in front of circular background, in Harris Studio
